  "stem": "<p>The table below shows three pairs of <i>x</i> and <i>y</i> values.</p><table border=\"1\"><tr><th><i>x</i></th><th><i>y</i></th></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>5</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>8</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>11</td></tr></table><p>Which of the following equations could represent the relationship between <i>x</i> and <i>y</i>?</p>",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<p><i>y</i> = 2<i>x</i> + 3</p>"
