  "rationale": "<p>Choice C is correct. The change in <i>y</i> per unit change in <i>x</i> is 3 (since <i>y</i> goes 5 &rarr; 8 &rarr; 11), so the slope is 3. Using (1, 5): 5 = 3(1) + <i>b</i>, so <i>b</i> = 2. Therefore <i>y</i> = 3<i>x</i> + 2.</p><p>Choices A, B, and D yield incorrect values when the listed <i>x</i> values are substituted.</p>",
